        <section id="id16801800">
          <title>DO YOU STILL REMEMBER?</title>
          <para id="id15573347">The answer to an addition sum is called the SUM.</para>
          <para id="id15580437">Thus: 4 873 + 2 168 = 7 041</para>
          <para id="id15647506"/>
          <para id="id16744377"> addend  addend  sum</para>
          <para id="id16725758">3. Some more mental calculation!</para>
          <para id="id7250293">Calculate the answers without using a calculator. Use the code and complete the following sentence:</para>
          <para id="id7671121">Subtraction is called the _____________________________________ of addition.</para>
          <para id="id7671127">3.1 27 + 35</para>
